\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527903\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 17, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104glj1665702919701.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/glj1665702919701.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/glj1665702919701.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"glj1665702919701\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Uniface Messages \n        </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Understand how Uniface messages are used (for example, message severity levels,\n                message numbering scheme, or how message text is displayed).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"glj1665702919701__p_d153062e1_d153063e1_d153064e1\">Uniface messages have the following severity levels:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"glj1665702919701__li_d53048e1_d53049e1_d53050e1\">Error messages—an action or event has caused an error in the application, preventing the action or event from continuing.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"glj1665702919701__li_d53051e1_d53052e1_d53053e1\">Warning messages—an action or event is likely to cause an error in the application, or if data is likely to be lost.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"glj1665702919701__li_d53054e1_d53055e1_d53056e1\">Information messages—provide feedback on the success or failure of an action or event, and provide information on the status of the application.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"glj1665702919701__p_d153065e1_d153066e1_d153067e1\">Uniface message share the same four-digit numbering scheme. You can use these numbers to refer to the documentation for information on the possible causes and solutions for errors and warnings, and for explanations of information messages.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"glj1665702919701__p_d153068e1_d153069e1_d153070e1\">Messages might be displayed in a pop-up dialog or in\n                        the Message Frame.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Refer to the following topics:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"glj1665702919701__ul_rsk_w44_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dff1665703279684.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dff1665703279684.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 0000-0999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xvn1665703304367.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xvn1665703304367.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 1000-1999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mug1665703385243.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mug1665703385243.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 2000-2999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tjb1665703391252.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tjb1665703391252.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 3000-3999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xmo1665703396183.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xmo1665703396183.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 4000-4999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"znw1665703398055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/znw1665703398055.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 5000-5999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qdv1665703403838.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qdv1665703403838.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 6000-6999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kwl1665703473176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kwl1665703473176.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 7000-7999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sxk1665703495801.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sxk1665703495801.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 8000-8999</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"the1665703520283.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/the1665703520283.html\" title=\"Refer to the Uniface message number, message text, and an explanation of the message.\">Uniface Messages 9000-9999</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527903\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527903\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface Messages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 17, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface Messages Understand how Uniface messages are used (for example, message severity levels, message numbering scheme, or how message text is displayed). Uniface messages have the following severity levels: Error messages—an action or event has caused an error in the application, preventing the action or event from continuing. Warning messages—an action or event is likely to cause an error in the application, or if data is likely to be lost. Information messages—provide feedback on the success or failure of an action or event, and provide information on the status of the application. Uniface message share the same four-digit numbering scheme. You can use these numbers to refer to the documentation for information on the possible causes and solutions for errors and warnings, and for explanations of information messages. Messages might be displayed in a pop-up dialog or in the Message Frame. Refer to the following topics: Uniface Messages 0000-0999 Uniface Messages 1000-1999 Uniface Messages 2000-2999 Uniface Messages 3000-3999 Uniface Messages 4000-4999 Uniface Messages 5000-5999 Uniface Messages 6000-6999 Uniface Messages 7000-7999 Uniface Messages 8000-8999 Uniface Messages 9000-9999 Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}